We recommended that the DCW Division:
strictly enforce the provisions in the Water Service Undertaking to consumers with delinquent accounts until all balances from prior and current years are paid;
determine past due accounts and include them in the Billing Statements;
upgrade or fully establish its software system to speed up monitoring delinquent accounts.

We recommended that the City Mayor:
transfer the authority of solid waste collection from GSO to CENRO to manage the solid waste based on the SWMP;
provide additional dump trucks and garbage collectors to accommodate the collection services needed by the remaining thirty barangays.

We recommended that:
City SWMB properly monitor, adopt revenue-generating measures, oversee and develop mechanics and guidelines for the implementation of the City SWMP;
CENRO coordinate with the Local Finance Committee to ensure that all relevant costs for the implementation of the SWMP is integrated to the Annual Budget as well as the Annual Investment Plan.

